Package core

Interface HlaLogicalTime

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<HlaLogicalTime>
    public interface HlaLogicalTime
extends java.lang.Comparable<HlaLogicalTime>
    A HlaLogicalTime is representation of the logical scenario time within the simulation. Note that the logical time might not be related to wall clock time or the HlaTimeStamp.

    This class is Immutable (and therefore ThreadSafe) as defined by Java Concurrency in Practice, see jcip.net.

    See Also:
    HlaTimeStamp
